# Peppermint

JSON data transformer for ReDBox

## Requirements

- JRE installation
- A Groovy installation

## Building

Install Gradle. Then run command: ` ./gradlew shadowJar`

## Running

### Via Docker
TODO: add set up info

### Running manually (from the dev environment, etc.)

Run command from project directory: `java -cp <path to groovy installation>/lib/*:./build/libs/peppermint-fat.jar io.vertx.core.Launcher`
